    "objective": "SEXTANT PME is a sub-fund that applies a discretionary strategy. Its objective is to outperform the benchmark (MSCI EMU (EuropeanEconomic and Monetary Union) Micro Cap Net Return EUR) through a selection of European SMEs. Its investment horizon is over five years. The sub-fund also aims to build a portfolio of companies demonstrating strong sustainability and governance practices, notably throughthe adoption of an ESG score improvement approach and by setting a minimum threshold for sustainable investments."
